commit.message: hackathon completed android
gvr-javascript: rename GVRBaseSensor to GVRSensor
Post-rebase updates
Modified demos for 4.1 API changes

Change cardboard-audio demo to use resonance audio extension (#575)

* Change cardboard-audio demo to use resonance audio extension

 * Change the demo to use ResonanceAudio extension.

GearVRf-DCO-1.0-Signed-off-by: Ragner Magalhaes <ragner.n@samsung.com>
GearVRf-DCO-1.0-Signed-off-by: Cristiano Bozzetto <c.bozzetto@samsung.com>

* audio simplification

* Fix cardboard build

GearVRf-DCO-1.0-Signed-off-by: Ragner Magalhaes <ragner.n@samsung.com>
gradle: backend tweaks
gvr-x3d-demo: use the x3d extension
gradle: add abiFilter so we can use the android profiler
gradle: rework the way backends are specified

Fixed demos to work with latest controller fixes (#556)

* gvr-3dcursor: fix disappearing cursor

cursor disappears after settings dialog because cursor.setEnable(true) won't call onEnable if it already is enabled. I fixed this.

* revert last fix

* Fix gv4-3dcursor selection buttons

* Change demos to use GVRTouchPadGestureListener

Demos had several different implementations of
VRTouchPadGestureDetector. We cannot legally distribute this class in
the Framework. Demos have been changed to use the new
GVRTouchPadGestureListener class which does pretty much the same thing
but in a different way. Now all these demos use the same class for this
functionality.

* Use GVREventReceiver for controller event dispatch

* Remove CursorUtils.java from gvr-remote-scripting

* gvr-accessibility: dont add cursor to scene

Let the input manager do it

* Make sendEventsToActivity the default

* gvr-widgetviewer: clean up the code

1. use GVRSwitch object to select between objects
2. isolate unused thumbnail code
3. refactor into multiple functions

* Daydream build for controller-ready demos

changed AndroidManifest.xml to include DAYDREAM intent for the apps which support the daydream controller

* Removed buildToolsVersion from build.gradle files

* Remove useControllerTypes from gvr.xml

To test the default of "gaze,controller" which is what these demos require

* fix reticle in gvr-controller demo
